statements: SELECT * FROM price_data;
SELECT token_id, price, volume FROM price_data WHERE exchange_id = 1;
SELECT timestamp, price FROM price_data WHERE token_id = 100 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT exchange_id, token_id FROM price_data WHERE price > 1000 ORDER BY token_id ASC;
SELECT MAX(price) AS highest_price, MIN(price) AS lowest_price FROM price_data;
SELECT * FROM price_data WHERE token_id = 123 ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT token_id, price FROM price_data WHERE price > 1000 ORDER BY price ASC, timestamp DESC;
SELECT DISTINCT exchange_id FROM price_data WHERE volume >= 50000;
SELECT token_id, AVG(price) AS avg_price FROM price_data GROUP BY token_id HAVING AVG(price) > 500 ORDER BY avg_price DESC;
SELECT exchange_id, COUNT(*) AS num_records FROM price_data GROUP BY exchange_id HAVING num_records >= 100 ORDER BY num_records DESC, exchange_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM decentralized_exchanges;
SELECT exchange_name, price FROM decentralized_exchanges WHERE price > 1000;
SELECT token_pair, price FROM decentralized_exchanges ORDER BY price DESC;
SELECT * FROM analyzed_prices WHERE analysis_date = '2022-01-15';
SELECT token_pair, AVG(average_price) AS avg_price FROM analyzed_prices GROUP BY token_pair;
SELECT * FROM decentralized_exchanges ORDER BY price DESC, time ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT exchange_name, price, time FROM decentralized_exchanges WHERE exchange_name = 'Uniswap' AND token_pair = 'ETH/USDT';
SELECT MAX(price), MIN(price), AVG(price) FROM decentralized_exchanges WHERE time >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT token_pair, COUNT(*) FROM decentralized_exchanges GROUP BY token_pair ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC;
SELECT de.exchange_name, ap.average_price FROM decentralized_exchanges de INNER JOIN analyzed_prices ap ON de.token_pair = ap.token_pair WHERE de.price > ap.highest_price ORDER BY de.price ASC;
SELECT * FROM decentralized_exchanges;
SELECT id, exchange_name, price FROM decentralized_exchanges WHERE price > 100;
SELECT exchange_name, token_name, price FROM decentralized_exchanges ORDER BY token_name DESC;
SELECT id, exchange_name, token_name, price FROM decentralized_exchanges WHERE exchange_name='Uniswap';
SELECT * FROM exchange_prices WHERE timestamp < '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM exchange_prices WHERE price > 100 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT exchange_name, token_name, price FROM decentralized_exchanges WHERE price < 50;
SELECT token_name, symbol FROM tokens ORDER BY token_name ASC, symbol DESC;
SELECT exchange_id, AVG(price) AS avg_price FROM exchange_prices GROUP BY exchange_id;
SELECT exchange_name, token_name, price FROM decentralized_exchanges WHERE exchange_name LIKE '%DEX%' AND token_name LIKE '%ETH%' ORDER BY price DESC;
SELECT * FROM decentralized_exchanges;
SELECT exchange_name, location FROM decentralized_exchanges;
SELECT exchange_name, location FROM decentralized_exchanges WHERE exchange_id = 1;
SELECT token_name, token_symbol FROM tokens;
SELECT token_name, token_symbol FROM tokens ORDER BY token_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM analysis_data ORDER BY average_price DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT exchange_name, location FROM decentralized_exchanges WHERE location = 'USA';
SELECT token_name, token_symbol FROM tokens WHERE token_name LIKE '%coin%';

SELECT exchange_name, location, token_name, price FROM decentralized_exchanges JOIN price_data ON decentralized_exchanges.exchange_id = price_data.exchange_id WHERE price > 100 ORDER BY price DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM tokens WHERE token_id IN (SELECT token_id FROM price_data WHERE price > 100) ORDER BY token_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM decentralized_exchanges;
SELECT id, name, location FROM decentralized_exchanges WHERE id = 1;
SELECT id, name, location FROM decentralized_exchanges ORDER BY name DESC;
SELECT symbol, name, decimal FROM tokens WHERE decimal > 8;
SELECT * FROM trades WHERE quantity > 10 ORDER BY price DESC;
SELECT * FROM decentralized_exchanges;
SELECT name, location FROM decentralized_exchanges ORDER BY name DESC;
SELECT tokens.name, prices.price FROM tokens JOIN prices ON tokens.id = prices.token_id WHERE prices.price > 100 ORDER BY prices.price ASC;
SELECT transactions.token_id, SUM(transactions.volume) AS total_volume FROM transactions GROUP BY transactions.token_id HAVING total_volume > 1000;

SELECT trades.quantity, prices.price FROM trades JOIN transactions ON trades.transaction_id = transactions.id JOIN prices ON transactions.token_id = prices.token_id WHERE trades.quantity * prices.price > 1000 ORDER BY trades.quantity DESC;
